OL,3,CChannel Islands experience hottest
OL,4,CJune on record
OL,6,FJersey and Guernsey have experienced
OL,7,Ftheir hottest Junes since records
OL,8,Fbegan, according to the islands' Met
OL,9,FOffices.
OL,11,FThe Channel Islands were approximately
OL,12,F3C hotter than they would normally be
OL,13,Fat this time of year.
OL,15,FJersey beat its previous warmest June
OL,16,Fby 0.5C and that record was set just
OL,17,Flast year.
OL,19,FThe previous warmest June in Guernsey
OL,20,Fwas recorded in 1846, 0.2C below the
OL,21,Fnew record.
