OL,3,CChannel Islands experience hottest
OL,4,CJune on record
OL,6,FAverage temperatures for June 2026:
OL,8,F30-year average June temperatures
OL,9,F(1991 to 2020):
OL,11,FAll data provided by Jersey and
OL,12,FGuernsey Met
OL,14,FLast week, both Bailiwicks experienced
OL,15,Fscorching temperatures in the second
OL,16,Fheatwave of the year.
OL,18,FIn Jersey, islanders faced a five-day
OL,19,Fheatwave between Sunday 21and Thursday
OL,20,F25 June.
