OL,3,CChannel Islands experience hottest
OL,4,CJune on record
OL,6,FFour consecutive days saw the mercury
OL,7,Fgo beyond 30C, with three tropical
OL,8,Fnights recorded in that time.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Guernsey experienced a four-
OL,11,Fday heatwave, starting on Monday 22
OL,12,FJune.
OL,14,FOn Thursday 25 June, both islands also
OL,15,Fmeasured their hottest days on record:
OL,17,FThe average June sea temperatures were
OL,18,Fthe warmest on record for that month,
OL,19,Fwith an average of 16.3C - 1.5C
OL,20,Fhigher than the 30-year long-term
OL,21,Faverage (1991 to 2020).
