OL,3,CChannel Islands experience hottest
OL,4,CJune on record
OL,6,FInterestingly, the wettest day this
OL,7,FJune was at the very beginning of the
OL,8,Fmonth.
OL,10,FAlmost two-thirds of Guernsey's
OL,11,Fmonthly rain came on 1 June, with
OL,12,FJersey garnering nearly half of its
OL,13,Frainfall on the same day.
